item.dc:creator: @Divinity Divinity
item.description:
@Divinity wrote:

You probably bugged your account, ask the owner to reset your items in your account. You probably spawned a item that doesn’t exist which can make your screen turn black. If this doesn’t work tell the owner to reset the server.
